  pages    = "W609--12",
  abstract = "PAL2NAL is a web server that constructs a multiple codon alignment
              from the corresponding aligned protein sequences. Such codon
              alignments can be used to evaluate the type and rate of nucleotide
              substitutions in coding DNA for a wide range of evolutionary
              analyses, such as the identification of levels of selective
