  number    =  43,
  pages     = "18201--18206",
  abstract  = "Reactive oxygen species (ROS) interact with DNA, frequently
               generating highly mutagenic 7,8-dihydro-8-oxoguanine (8-oxo-G)
               lesions. Replicative DNA polymerases (pols) often misincorporate
