  journal  = "J. Biol. Chem.",
  volume   =  278,
  number   =  40,
  pages    = "38121--38124",
  abstract = "To evaluate the antimutagenic role of a mammalian mutY homolog,
              namely the Mutyh gene, which encodes adenine DNA glycosylase
              excising adenine misincorporated opposite 8-oxoguanine in the
              template DNA, we generated MUTYH-null mouse embryonic stem (ES)
