              separate. These processes are linked to heterochromatic mo-2
              minisatellite arrays, and require MEI4 and ANKRD31 proteins but
              not the axis components REC8 or HORMAD1. We propose that the
              repetitive DNA sequence of the PAR confers unique chromatin and
              higher-order structures that are crucial for recombination.
