              framework that effectively addresses these questions. Our approach
              provides a basis for characterizing mutational signatures from
              cancer-derived somatic mutational catalogs, paving the way to
              insights into the pathogenetic mechanism underlying all cancers.",
  month    =  jan,
  year     =  2013,
  language = "en"
}

@ARTICLE{Edge2017-ae,
  title    = "{HapCUT2}: robust and accurate haplotype assembly for diverse
