  volume   =  101,
  number   =  3,
  pages    = "369--390",
  abstract = "Genetic risk factors for autism spectrum disorder (ASD) have yet
              to be fully elucidated. Postzygotic mosaic mutations (PMMs) have
              been implicated in several neurodevelopmental disorders and
              overgrowth syndromes. By leveraging whole-exome sequencing data on
